
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ms">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jemputan Kahwin: Firdaus & Aisyah</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        /* SWAT THEME CSS (Black, Dark Slate, Turquoise/Cyan Accent, White Text) */
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0a0f12;         /* Deep SWAT Tactical Black */
            --bg-card: #121b20;         /* Dark Slate Card */
            --primary: #00f0ff;         /* Neon Tactical Turquoise */
            --primary-hover: #00b3bf;   /* Deeper Turquoise */
            --text-light: #f3f4f6;      /* Off-white */
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;      /* Muted Gray */
            --gold: #d4af37;            /* Minimal Elegant touch */
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-light);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Ambient Background Grid Pattern */
        .ambient-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.03) 0%, transparent 40%);
            z-index: -2;
        }

        .grid-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
                              linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        /* Audio Controls */
        .audio-control {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 25px;
            right: 25px;
            background: rgba(18, 27, 32, 0.85);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            color: var(--primary);
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .audio-control:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.6);
        }

        /* Overlay/Envelope Cover */
        #envelope {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #162229 0%, #06090a 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: transform 1s cubic-bezier(0.85, 0, 0.15, 1);
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
        }

        #envelope.opened {
            transform: translateY(-100%);
        }

        .envelope-content {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .tactical-badge {
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--primary);
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15);
            animation: pulse-border 2s infinite;
        }

        .envelope-title {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .envelope-names {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-open {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 12px 35px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .btn-open:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.5);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Main Container */
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* Header / Hero Section */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .arabic-phrase {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .english-salut {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        /* Corner tactical markings (SWAT Theme style) */
        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--primary);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }
        .card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary);
            border-right: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .card-corner-tr {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--primary);
            border-right: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .card-corner-bl {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .parents-section p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .parent-names {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin: 15px 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .invitation-text {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .bride-groom {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .name-wrapper {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .couple-name {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .ampersand {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        /* Event Details */
        .details-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        @media(min-width: 600px) {
            .details-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .detail-box {
            background: rgba(10, 15, 18, 0.6);
            border: 1px dashed rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.25);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .detail-box:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .detail-box i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .detail-box h3 {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .detail-box p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .detail-box span {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            display: block;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Countdown Timer */
        .countdown-title {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .countdown-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .countdown-item {
            background: #0d161c;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            min-width: 75px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .countdown-number {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            display: block;
        }

        .countdown-label {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Itinerary / Atur Cara Majlis */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 30px auto 0 auto;
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 5px;
            width: 2px;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 6px;
            left: -19px;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--primary);
        }

        .timeline-time {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .timeline-desc {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Map Section and Navigation Buttons */
        .map-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .btn-nav {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(18, 27, 32, 0.9);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .btn-nav:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-nav i {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* Pantun Section */
        .pantun-section {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            position: relative;
        }

        .pantun-section i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15);
            position: absolute;
            top: -20px;
            left: 10px;
        }

        /* RSVP Form Section */
        .rsvp-form-container {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .form-input, .form-select, .form-textarea {
            width: 100%;
            background: #0a0f12;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-input:focus, .form-select:focus, .form-textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.25);
        }

        .btn-submit {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            border: none;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.6);
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .rsvp-contacts {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .contact-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: rgba(10, 15, 18, 0.5);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .contact-info {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .contact-name {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .contact-num {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .btn-call {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
            color: var(--primary);
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-call:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* Guestbook Section */
        .guestbook-list {
            margin-top: 25px;
            max-height: 250px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-right: 5px;
        }

        /* Scrollbar Styling */
        .guestbook-list::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 5px;
        }
        .guestbook-list::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #0a0f12;
        }
        .guestbook-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .guest-wish {
            background: rgba(10, 15, 18, 0.7);
            border-left: 2px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in;
        }

        .guest-name {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .guest-text {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .guest-time {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .footer-quote {
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Alert/Notification Modal */
        .modal {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.9);
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            z-index: 2000;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.5);
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
        }

        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            z-index: 1999;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal-overlay.active {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .modal-btn {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal-btn:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--primary);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes pulse-border {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Hide Audio Element */
        audio {
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Ambient Grid & Glows -->
    <div class="ambient-bg"></div>
    <div class="grid-overlay"></div>

    <!-- Background Audio (Premium Instrumental Piano) -->
    <audio id="bg-music" loop>
        <!-- Royalty free elegant background music -->
        <source src="https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-1.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
        Pemain audio tidak disokong oleh pelayar anda.
    </audio>

    <!-- Interactive Envelope/Cover -->
    <div id="envelope">
        <div class="envelope-content">
            <span class="tactical-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-crosshairs"></i> JEMPUTAN KAHWIN INTERAKTIF</span>
            <h1 class="envelope-title">WALIMATULURUS</h1>
            <div class="envelope-names">Firdaus & Aisyah</div>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">Ahad, 15 Jun 2026</p>
            <p style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 10px; text-transform: uppercase;">Dewan Seri Impian, Kajang</p>
            <button class="btn-open" onclick="openEnvelope()">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Buka Jemputan
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Audio Control Button Floating -->
    <div class="audio-control" id="audioToggle" onclick="toggleAudio()">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-volume-xmark" id="audioIcon"></i>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Wrapper -->
    <div class="wrapper">
        
        <!-- Header -->
        <header>
            <div class="arabic-phrase">بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ</div>
            <div class="english-salut">ASSALAMUALAIKUM WARAHMATULLAHI WABARAKATUH</div>
        </header>

        <!-- Parents Section -->
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-corner-tr"></div>
            <div class="card-corner-bl"></div>
            
            <div class="parents-section">
                <p>Dengan penuh rasa syukur ke hadrat Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta’ala serta memohon limpah kurnia dan rahmat-Nya yang berpanjangan, maka dengan segala hormat dan takzimnya,</p>
                
                <h2 class="parent-names">Yang Berbahagia Tuan Haji Ahmad bin Abdullah</h2>
                <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--primary); margin: 5px 0;">&</p>
                <h2 class="parent-names">Yang Berbahagia Puan Hajah Siti Zaleha binti Ismail</h2>
                
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;">seisi keluarga,</p>
                <p class="invitation-text">menjemput dengan penuh sukacita dan berbesar hati akan kehadiran Dato’ / Datin / Tuan / Puan / Encik / Cik ke</p>
                
                <p style="text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star-of-life"></i> MAJLIS PERSANDINGAN PUTERA DAN PUTERI KAMI
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Couple Section -->
            <div class="bride-groom">
                <div class="name-wrapper">
                    <h2 class="couple-name">Muhammad Firdaus bin Ahmad</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="ampersand">dengan</div>
                <div class="name-wrapper">
                    <h2 class="couple-name">Nur Aisyah binti Mohd Razali</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Countdown Timer Card -->
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-corner-tr"></div>
            <div class="card-corner-bl"></div>
            <div class="countdown-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> KIRA DETIK MAJLIS</div>
